pageContext.claim: “The reason the Democrats don't want to submit the Articles of Impeachment to the Senate is that they don't want corrupt politician Adam Shifty Schiff to testify under oath, nor do they want the Whistleblower, the missing second Whistleblower, the informer, the Bidens, to testify!”
pageContext.analysis: Democrats held onto the impeachment articles for four weeks in order to get more assurances on Senate procedures, not because they were afraid of which witnesses might be called to testify. They had been arguing for relevant witnesses.
